**OOP Exercises - Kotlin & Dart**

A hands-on collection of Object-Oriented Programming exercises 
implemented in both Kotlin and Dart. This project was built to
practice and compare core OOP concepts across two modern 
programming languages.

*About the Project*
This folder contains 3 OOP exercises, each implemented in
both Kotlin and Dart. The goal is to:
-Strengthen understanding of OOP fundamentals,
-See how the same concepts are expressed in two different 
 languages,
-Practice using abstract classes, sealed classes, and interfaces.
